snippet.title: Power Racer - Game Boy
snippet.description:
For more Nintendo Game Boy gameplays, check out my playlist here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLd_OVXFXzJ5WNIzYSSrrUUxiasW6rEK0y

FINALLY!  My first upload for the legendary Game Boy handheld system...and, Tetris aside, this is perhaps my favourite GB game ever.

Sound emulation may not be 100%, but given what I had to go through to get a decent video uploaded here, I'm taking it as gold!
